Class LengthController

java.lang.Object
org.heigit.ohsome.ohsomeapi.controller.dataaggregation.elements.LengthController
@RestController @RequestMapping("/elements/length") public class LengthController extends Object
Controller containing the GET and POST request handling methods, which are mapped to "/elements/length".
